tool_description:
MEET TAXEE

Your Friendly Neighborhood Income Tax Data and Calculation API.
name: Taxee
title: Taxee

api_list.name: Get Federal Income Tax Information
api_list.description: Given a year, returns tax brackets and deductions for all filing statuses.

required_parameters.name: year
required_parameters.description: The year of the federal income tax information you'd like to request.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://stylinandy-taxee.p.rapidapi.com/v1/federal/2014"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "stylinandy-taxee.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: V2 - Get State Income Tax Information

required_parameters.name: year

required_parameters.name: state
required_parameters.description: The abbreviation of the state whose data you're requesting.
